source.sqlReaderQuery:
SELECT *
FROM [MSL_999].[MSL_ISSUE_TRACKER_LOGS]
WHERE CAST([CLIENT_ISSUE_LOG_DATE] AS DATE) = 
    (SELECT MAX(CAST([CLIENT_ISSUE_LOG_DATE] AS DATE)) 
     FROM [MSL_999].[MSL_ISSUE_TRACKER_LOGS])
AND ISDATE([CLIENT_ISSUE_LOG_DATE]) = 1;
